### 第一层

$$
\begin{align*}
&\theta = \left(\begin{array}{cccccccc}1 & 0 & 0 & -1 & 0 & 0 & -1 & 1\end{array}\right) \\
\Rightarrow
&\begin{cases}
\alpha &= \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1 & 0 & 0 & -1 \end{array}\right)\\
\beta &= \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 0 & -1 & 0 & 1 \end{array}\right)
\end{cases} \\
&W = 1 \\
\Rightarrow
&\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &= \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1 & -1 & 0 & 0 \end{array}\right)\\
\varphi_2 &= \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1 & 1 & 0 & -2 \end{array}\right)
\end{cases} \\
\Rightarrow
&\theta = \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1 & -1 & 0 & 0\\ 1 & 1 & 0 & -2 \end{array}\right) \rightarrow \left(\begin{array}{cccc} C(0) & D(0) & E(0) & F(0)\\ C(1) & D(1) & E(1) & F(1) \end{array}\right)
\end{align*}
$$

### 第二层

$$
\begin{align*}
&\theta = \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1 & -1 & 0 & 0\\ 1 & 1 & 0 & -2 \end{array}\right) \\
\Rightarrow
&\begin{cases}
\alpha &= \left(\begin{array}{cc} 1 & 0\\ 1 & 0 \end{array}\right)\\
\beta &= \left(\begin{array}{cc} -1 & 0\\ 1 & -2 \end{array}\right)
\end{cases} \\
&W = \left(\begin{array}{cc} 1 & 0\\ 0 & -\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right) \\
\Rightarrow
&\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &= \left(\begin{array}{cc} 0 & 0\\ 1-\mathrm{i} & 2{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right)\\
\varphi_2 &= \left(\begin{array}{cc} 2 & 0\\ 1+1{}\mathrm{i} & -2{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right)
\end{cases} \\
\Rightarrow
&\theta = \left(\begin{array}{cc} 0 & 0\\ 1-\mathrm{i} & 2{}\mathrm{i}\\ 2 & 0\\ 1+1{}\mathrm{i} & -2{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right) \rightarrow \left(\begin{array}{cc} A(0) & B(0)\\ A(1) & B(1)\\ A(2) & B(2)\\ A(3) & B(3) \end{array}\right)
\end{align*}
$$

div.data-content:
### 第三层

$$
\begin{align*}
&\theta = \left(\begin{array}{cc} 0 & 0\\ 1-\mathrm{i} & 2{}\mathrm{i}\\ 2 & 0\\ 1+1{}\mathrm{i} & -2{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right) \\
\Rightarrow
&\begin{cases}
\alpha &= \left(\begin{array}{c} 0\\ 1-\mathrm{i}\\ 2\\ 1+1{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right)\\
\beta &= \left(\begin{array}{c} 0\\ 2{}\mathrm{i}\\ 0\\ -2{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right)
\end{cases} \\
&W = \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1 & 0 & 0 & 0\\ 0 & \sqrt{2}\,\left(\frac{1}{2}-\frac{1}{2}{}\mathrm{i}\right) & 0 & 0\\ 0 & 0 & -\mathrm{i} & 0\\ 0 & 0 & 0 & \sqrt{2}\,\left(-\frac{1}{2}-\frac{1}{2}{}\mathrm{i}\right) \end{array}\right) \\
\Rightarrow
&\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &= \left(\begin{array}{c} 0\\ \sqrt{2}\,\left(1+1{}\mathrm{i}\right)+1-\mathrm{i}\\ 2\\ 1+\sqrt{2}\,\left(-1+1{}\mathrm{i}\right)+1{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right)\\
\varphi_2 &= \left(\begin{array}{c} 0\\ 1+\sqrt{2}\,\left(-1-\mathrm{i}\right)-\mathrm{i}\\ 2\\ \sqrt{2}\,\left(1-\mathrm{i}\right)+1+1{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right)
\end{cases} \\
\Rightarrow
&\theta = \left(\begin{array}{c} 0\\ \sqrt{2}\,\left(1+1{}\mathrm{i}\right)+1-\mathrm{i}\\ 2\\ 1+\sqrt{2}\,\left(-1+1{}\mathrm{i}\right)+1{}\mathrm{i}\\ 0\\ 1+\sqrt{2}\,\left(-1-\mathrm{i}\right)-\mathrm{i}\\ 2\\ \sqrt{2}\,\left(1-\mathrm{i}\right)+1+1{}\mathrm{i} \end{array}\right) \rightarrow \left(\begin{array}{c} X(0)\\ X(1)\\ X(2)\\ X(3)\\ X(4)\\ X(5)\\ X(6)\\ X(7) \end{array}\right)
\end{align*}
$$
